## Loading Pattern

**Router → This Index → Language Router/Index → Subcategory Index → Files**

1. Root Router detects "backend" or language keyword → loads this index
2. This index routes to language router/index based on detected language
3. Language router/index routes to subcategory indexes (language/, architecture/, data/, etc.)
4. Subcategory indexes point to specific rule files

